race.description: Greg Horan Construction Pty Ltd Hcp (C2)
race.comment: WIFE SAYS YES (9) settled back in the run last start and closed off strongly last time out. Third-up now and out to the mile looks ideal and she may be able to hold a closer spot on settling. Hasn't won for a while but put the writing on the wall last start and can end the drought now. RAZMAS (2) was too strong last start, making every post a winner to score in a photo finish over 1400m here. He may be able to dictate the speed once again from the draw and he was solid over this trip at Belmont two back. Can repeat the dose without surprising. TITAN RISING (5) was behind RAZMAS last time out, finishing 5.3L off the winner, though getting out in trip looks a big key to his chances. He's raced well under similar circumstances at Penola four starts back and he's not out of this on his best form. MORIAH (12) can improve getting out in distance today. NADELL (10) can bounce back third-up today.
